      "para_id": "Q001861.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Ibbi-Suen , the god of the Land , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Dada , the governor of Nibru , child of Ur-Nanibgal , the governor of Nibru , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
